Usage: generateLef [-help] <outputLefFile> [-clfFile <clffile>]
                   [-lefFile <lefFile>] [-lefFileList <fileList>] [-noWE]
                   [-techFile <techFile>]

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
<outputLefFile>          # output lef file name (string, required)
-clfFile <clffile>       # clf file name. (string, optional)
-lefFile <lefFile>       # lef file name. (string, optional)
-lefFileList <fileList>  # lef file list (string, optional)
-noWE                    # generate default vias for no wire extension routing
                         # (bool, optional)
-techFile <techFile>     # tech file name. (string, optional)